  "intent": "Execute NEBNext Ultra II RNA Library Prep Kit Section 1: Perform poly(A) RNA isolation using oligo-dT magnetic beads with 8-48 samples. Mix 50\u00b5L beads with RNA samples, denature at 65\u00b0C for 5min, bind poly(A) RNA for 5min, perform magnetic separation and two 180\u00b5L wash buffer washes, elute in 50\u00b5L Tris buffer at 80\u00b0C for 2min, rebind with 50\u00b5L 2X binding buffer, perform final wash, and elute in 11.5\u00b5L first strand reaction buffer with random primers. Fragment at 94\u00b0C for 15min and collect final 10\u00b5L eluate for cDNA synthesis.",
